object.customQuery:
select
	distinct
	stg.system_id as system_id,
	stg.parent_id as parent_id,
	stg.cmm_container as cmm_container,
	stg.id as id,
	stg.name as name,
	stg.value as value,
	stg.visible_ind as visible_indicator,
	stg.text as text,
	stg.display_desc as display_description,
	stg.row_id as row_id,
	tgt.acx_question_reply_row_id,
	tgt.acx_question_reply_row_md5checksum 
from
	dbo.underwriting_dashboard_question_reply_stg stg
	left join bronze.acx_question_reply tgt 
	on stg.system_id = tgt.system_id 
	and stg.cmm_container = tgt.cmm_container 
	and stg.id = tgt.id 
	and acx_question_reply_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
order by system_id, cmm_container ;

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: src_md5_hash_value
fields.expression:
MD5(
'system_id' || to_char(system_id) ||
'parent_id' || parent_id ||
'cmm_container' || cmm_container ||
'id' || id ||
'name' || name ||
'value' || value ||
'visible_indicator' || visible_indicator ||
'text' || text ||
'display_description' || display_description ||
'row_id' || to_char(row_id)
)
